{"title":"Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #6: Condor Leggero","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-6-condor-leggero","date":1741091714000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-6-condor-leggero\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #6: Condor Leggero</a></p>\n\n<p>Whether you’re looking for a new bike or just want to try out some of the best bikes in the world, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days</a> offer a unique experience to test the latest top-end bikes from the leading brands on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The next bike in our run-through of some of the incredible bikes that you can test ride at this years Track Days is the Condor Leggero.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Produced by legendary London brand Condor, the Leggero is an <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-all-round-road-race-bikes\">all-round road bike</a> with its light weight and aero-accented frame. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Cyclist</em>‘s writer Laurence Kilpatrick reviewed the Condor Leggero last year and liked its ‘considered combination of cycling heritage and modern racing sensibilities’.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Laurence tested the build with a Campagnolo Super Record Wireless groupset and Campagnolo Bora Ultra WTO 45 wheels, which is priced at £11,593, and it weighed in at 7.3kg.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can read Laurence’s full review <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/condor-leggero-road-bike-review-2024\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Condor Leggero will be at the following Track Days events:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>26<sup>th</sup> April 2025, Odd Down Cycle Track Bath,<br />17<sup>th</sup> May 2025, Lee Valley VeloPark London,<br />7<sup>th</sup> June 2025, The Brownlee Centre, Leeds</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information on Cyclist Track Days click <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/cyclist-track-days-2025-3855053\" target=\"_blank\">BOOK YOUR TICKET HERE</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-trek-madone-slr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #5: Trek Madone SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-factor-ostro-vam\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #3: Factor Ostro VAM</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-van-rysel-rcr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #1: Van Rysel RCR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 info and how to get tickets</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/condor-leggero-road-bike-review-2024\">Condor Leggero road